metadata.name: DESTINY
metadata.description:
the artist's success is his muse

a muse that inspires, intoxicates with ideas, elevates to heaven

the creator will never refuse a muse if one day she captivated him, because his work lives and breathes thanks to her

having met my muse, I finally understood the meaning of this beautiful word

since then, all my creations has gained a new life, meaning, and I discovered my destiny
